Class NavalBattleResults

java.lang.Object
  robocode.BattleResults
      robocode.NavalBattleResults
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<BattleResults>
Direct Known Subclasses:
ShipResults
public class NavalBattleResults
extends BattleResults

Contains the Naval version of the battle results returned by BattleEndedEvent.getResults() when a battle has ended. Technically the same as BattleResults, but with the added bonus of mineDamage and mineBonus.

Since:
1.9.2.2
Author:
Thales B.V. / Thomas Hakkers
See Also:
BattleEndedEvent.getResults(), Ship.onBattleEnded(BattleEndedEvent), Serialized Form
